=========================================================
                PCP client library
=========================================================

PCP client library implements client side of PCP stack (RFC 6887). It enables
any network application to manage network edge device using PCP (e.g. to create
NAT mapping or ask router for specific flow treatment).

There are also other PCP command line tools included::

Components:
    - libpcp     - PCP client library
    - pcp_app    - PCP client CLI app
    - pcp_server - mock PCP server
    - scapy      - PCP layer for Scapy

Build instructions are located in INSTALL file. More information about
components are in each subdirectory's README file.

